<h1>Jaktia component library</h1>
<p>This is the component library for Jaktia. **Feel free to look around!**</p>

<h2>Component categories</h2>
<p>All components are ordered according to the <a href="http://bradfrost.com/blog/post/atomic-web-design/" target="_blank">Atomic design pattern</a>. There's one extra folder added called Master layouts which contains the main layouts of the site.</p>

